flowchart TD
    A[Backend/Admin gui POST /train<br/>modelName, nlu, stories,<br/>rules, domain, actions, firetune] --> B[Flask API validate request<br/>va kiem tra training_status]
    B --> C[Ghi nlu.yml, stories.yml,<br/>rules.yml, domain.yml]
    C --> D{Co actions moi?}
    D -- Co --> E[Rewrite actions.py<br/>va restart Action Server]
    D -- Khong --> F[Bo qua buoc actions]
    E --> G[Khoi tao train command]
    F --> G
    G --> H{firetune = true?}
    H -- Co --> I[python -m rasa train<br/>--epoch-fraction 0.5]
    H -- Khong --> J[python -m rasa train]
    I --> K[Background training thread<br/>cap nhat training_status = training]
    J --> K
    K --> L[Model .tar.gz sinh ra trong models/]
    L --> M[Upload model len MinIO]
    M --> N[Cap nhat URL/model info vao MongoDB]
    N --> O[GET /training-status = completed]
    O --> P[Backend goi POST /run-model<br/>de load model moi vao Rasa]
